  "body": "\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n- Tests\n  - Added a CI workflow that repeatedly runs changed Go tests on PRs, detects flaky and consistently failing tests, posts a summary to the PR, and uploads detailed run artifacts.\n  - Modified a test to occasionally fail at runtime to surface intermittent instability.\n- Chores\n  - Added runner hardening and concurrency safeguards to the CI workflow.\n  - No user-facing functionality changes.\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
